      "description": "`netlify.toml` defines the dashboard build (`turbo run build --filter penny-dashboard`) and Next plugin, while `apps/dashboard/vercel.json` specifies framework, output directory, and npm-based install/build. It is unclear which platform is authoritative for production, which affects env var naming, build commands, and review of deployment safety.",
